          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Run loop sources come in two versions with different-sized context structures. ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "context",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " must point to the correct version of the structure for ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "source",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Before calling this function, you need to initialize the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "version",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " member of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "context",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " with the version number (either 0 or 1) of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "source",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
